So, I main Garen, i'm not to shabby with him, i'll have my good games and my bad ones but when I share my awesome scores with my friends 22/2/14 they say stuff like "Soon I will be able to play a skill based champ like Garen" or "You need more skill than garen to play lol"
I say if you get kills you obviously dont need to play a "Skill based champ" but noooo.
What do you guys think? {{champion:86}}
